					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12112722#post-4286695</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12112722/scp-4732#post-4286695</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2019 18:31:29 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Ohsahi</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5251519</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I saw it as a way to mess with time loops and experiment with the effects of physical changes to the record - I originally had a lot of other logs/tests, but realized that the Foundation would likely avoid most testing in order to keep the anomaly under wraps - the scratch was the only one I wrote that wouldn't breach secrecy.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
